{"tid":2259703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"九龍塘喇沙小學廁所遭縱火　 1000名師生自行疏散無人傷","createTime":"2020-10-27T04:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T05:00:43.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8ea8d2548c3354fed52bb7f1fc4a68f98bbd75b3","tid":2259703,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T04:36:11.000Z","msg":"九龍塘喇沙小學遭縱火。今（27日）早上8時，九龍塘喇沙利道喇沙小學樓上一個男廁內的毛巾起火，消防員到場，迅速將火救熄。經初步調查，起火原因有可疑，交由警方跟進，案件列縱火處理，交由九龍城警區刑事調查隊第五隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。火警期間1000名師生自行疏散，無人受傷。"},{"pid":"01e32662131a1993490e73fa479bcd630174d3e0","tid":2259703,"uid":65638,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T04:42:07.000Z","msg":"通常呢d 事班教畜會尻up 話，已經俾cctv 影倒你入廁所，個時間同起火時間好吻合，依家俾機會位同事，坦白從寬。 希望個小學生有上連登，老閪都唔好認，仲要搞多幾個火頭，分散班仆街注意力"},{"pid":"66d3e459933505d10a6da6b78f827694102a2464","tid":2259703,"uid":60563,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T04:45:41.000Z","msg":"「多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」"},{"pid":"d77f440b38708d72fca9ebccd3dd6ed99dcb0cf2","tid":2259703,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T04:46:26.000Z","msg":"一次食兩枝煙"},{"pid":"713194fb3184be33c90ebf1c43078fedb645eec1","tid":2259703,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T04:53:54.000Z","msg":"師弟仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e5f4296eb1dde8fcaa996bba22d3add90748eda","tid":2259703,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T04:56:06.000Z","msg":"半日都有1000人返？"},{"pid":"1fdaf621ac538fabfbfcc9efad453eb221e5399f","tid":2259703,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:00:43.000Z","msg":"壞過凱婷"}]}